The <u>Resource mode</u> is especially important! Use it to gather <color=#ffffff>wood</color> from trees and <color=#ffffff>carbon</color> from resource rocks <u>early on</u> to <color=#ffffff>build your first shelter</color> as soon as possible! You can also use it to destroy plants, stones and other obstacles that are in your way or prevent you from picking something up! 

Would you like to see a more detailed video about the Survival Tool and its working modes?

