English:
@q0 @d0Open the Blueprint Libary (<color=#44ff00>F2</color>). Select the tab '<color=#ffffff>PREFABS</color>' on the left side <color=#00ffff>( 1 )</color>. Set the filter '<color=#ffffff>Hover Vessel</color>' <color=#00ffff>( 2 )</color>. Enter the word '<color=#ffffff>Frame</color>' in the search field <color=#00ffff>( 3 )</color>. Select a <color=#ffffff>HV Frame A</color> and click the '<color=#ffffff>TO FACTORY</color>' <color=#00ffff>( 4 )</color> button on the <color=#ffffff>lower right</color> screen.

In the new window, drag all materials, for example the <color=#ffffff>Carbon Substrate</color> from your inventory into the '<color=#ffffff>INTAKE</color>' box <color=#00ffff>( 5 )</color>. When all requirements are <color=#44ff00>GREEN</color> <color=#00ffff>( 6 )</color>, press <color=#ffffff>START PRODUCTION</color> <color=#00ffff>( 7 )</color>. 
